{"tid":2496406,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"三十秒科學–喜馬拉雅山脈的紅色湖泊","createTime":"2021-04-19T21:43:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-19T21:51:55.000Z","uid":38861,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"74a5584eb199c4f04ea9f6325a1ac9affd832c31","tid":2496406,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T21:43:43.000Z","msg":"當湖水或海水受到藻類或微生物感染的時候，水的顏色便會變成紅色一片。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmP1EGNfm6PH4uyjbbZFHn7yweMKZutrFyKYdAM34s2jvC?filename=DPNPLXf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDPNPLXf.jpg&h=fe45eff5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而除了藻類感染之外，大自然間亦有著長年累月呈紅色的湖泊。<br />\n<br />\n(圖2)在喜馬拉雅山脈位置34&deg;0.280&prime;N 76&deg;43.295&prime;E，就有著一道長年累月均為棕紅色的湖泊。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmThpwuL6kPG29NhmpF8m5JvQmnqUo82kUoMbRExYr8Lvo?filename=ehHcJJZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FehHcJJZ.png&h=8d369478&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n該湖泊海拔5060米高，低氧、高紫外線及寒冷集於一身，冬天平均溫度攝氏-16，夏天平均溫度攝氏-6。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n(圖3)紅湖的形成，相信是由於湖水含有高濃度的氯氣，與周遭岩石的鐵離子產生化學反應，形成棕紅色的針鐵礦 (Goethite)及赤鐵礦 (Hematite)等。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmRv72fSqB2GdQmaXCYtNzyEzFzaKuKAUCCVEwEtAvtF1Z?filename=5oFxJJ4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5oFxJJ4.png&h=76c97ba5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但是紅湖的不遠處有著藍色的湖泊，為何它又不會呈棕紅色的呢?<br />\n那就有待有心人上山採樣本發掘真相了。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單俾一個like以及Bookmark，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=gloDjMIS9Xq41mamnCswuM5RZDHrhPshgzcG8Nqr5vw%3D&h=29e36a12\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「買一嚿/半嚿薯仔」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=gloDjMIS9Xq41mamnCswuM5RZDHrhPshgzcG8Nqr5vw%3D&h=6de72b6b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除非Facebook及IG重開侵侵的account，否則我的IG將不會再作更新，只會寄居本土LIHKG及Penana。<br />\n <br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://www.currentscience.ac.in/Volumes/120/02/0429.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.currentscience.ac.in%2FVolumes%2F120%2F02%2F0429.pdf&d=gloDjMIS9Xq41mamnCswuM5RZDHrhPshgzcG8Nqr5vw%3D&h=2817bdf3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.currentscience.ac.in/Volumes/120/02/0429.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"a4e48d2b270c72a3f4bae0956718885e5a9b6f65","tid":2496406,"uid":258356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T21:45:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />薯巴早晨"},{"pid":"6471a0ae12de286aaded5e4f4c702faf7acf4b89","tid":2496406,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a4e48d2b270c72a3f4bae0956718885e5a9b6f65","tid":2496406,"uid":258356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T21:45:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />薯巴早晨"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T21:46:43.000Z","msg":"早晨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55c46718076b7d21980f962b438f114623753875","tid":2496406,"uid":199689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T21:50